---

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle radial glow -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-blue-600/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
      Operasional bisnis mulai terasa padat?<br class="hidden sm:block" />
      <span class="text-blue-400">Bantu sistem Anda lebih rapi.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-base mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Akordium membantu bisnis kecil-menengah bekerja lebih tertata melalui website dan sistem informasi yang praktis, terstruktur, dan mudah dipakai sehari-hari.
    </p>

    <a
      href="/contact"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/30 text-sm mt-6"
    >
      Jadwalkan konsultasi
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
